data.description: Beautiful home in quiet neighborhood on nice flat yard close to the University. Walk in to a big inviting living room with cathedral ceiling and huge open pass through to the open concept kitchen. Kitchen has plenty of counter top space, tons of cabinets, pantry, eat in area, gas range and stainless steel appliances including fridge (WAO). Large master with dual vanities in ensuite and large walk in closet. All living areas have wood laminate flooring. Other bedrooms are large and a seperate laundry room.
